msgstr "Engagement en temps"

#: ../../admin/upgrading.rst:149
msgid ""
"Running all of the listed upgrades `took about 1 hour and 15 minutes`__ on "
"the Elgg community site which at the time had to migrate:"
msgstr "Exécuter l'ensemble de ces mises à niveau a demandé `environ 1 heure et 15 minutes`__ sur le site de la communauté Elgg qui contenait au moment de la migration :"

